  "body": "<p>One of the best parts about working with Amy these past couple of years has been her willingness to let me photograph so much of her life. Today I thought it would be fun to share some of favorite moments that we've been able to capture thus far! </p><p><strong>We documented her ever-growing bump:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"13a-amy.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598687229127-FUZF1XR823AJA0C2J6T5/13a-amy.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"13b-amy1.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598687228582-DZ91ZJV859T2GTCG6BNV/13b-amy1.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"13c-amy15.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598687229313-JMNSWQK0X5RWGLRWWEBZ/13c-amy15.jpg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Which later turned into her ever-growing baby Jack:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"13d-amy8.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598687268195-GIQBM0B728J7OFEH3T5K/13d-amy8.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"13e-amy3.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598687268292-OXAXR2X67DUZ00I9JWIY/13e-amy3.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"13f-amy2.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598687269278-GS4J4EKFX4NOONURUPOF/13f-amy2.jpg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p><strong>We rounded up the family for a few impromptu portraits:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"13g-amy4.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598687333609-1B2N6IFJ9WY7Q01Q3YQ3/13g-amy4.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"13h-amy5.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598687333602-AG1UWWVPQXCWRURD7FK7/13h-amy5.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"13i-amy6.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598687334164-SFEPCSGE97YKN49MESB5/13i-amy6.jpg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p><strong>We wandered around town:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"13j-amy10.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598687367502-STU6L93Y2AINJRFREGO5/13j-amy10.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"13k-amy_dogs.gif\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598687370762-GORJ319CHPRTEQ0WO3I5/13k-amy_dogs.gif\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"13l-lundeens_2.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598687368329-2U4JER630QTYUEQHKL9X/13l-lundeens_2.jpg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p><strong>We hung out in her studio:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"13m-amy13.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598687410056-6THFG3ZW5RQLHHOUHGDZ/13m-amy13.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"13n-amy12.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598687410171-2MVK0HITMFO7W7ZPOWWL/13n-amy12.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"13o-amy14.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598687410457-Q2GXSGCXH0ODUK32LEB0/13o-amy14.jpg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p><strong>We then moved to </strong><a href=\"https://amy-tan-z6av.squarespace.com/amy-tangerine/2014/04/house-tour.html\"><strong>the house</strong></a><strong> for a snack break:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"13p-house_6-600x442.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598687451862-EGZC0O048HCH1IO7TG3R/13p-house_6-600x442.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"13q-jack_10-600x400.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598687451806-JVABY99ATG2HXEI085PY/13q-jack_10-600x400.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"13r-house_1-600x441.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598687452218-WWINEGNPI14CJ63DNO5X/13r-house_1-600x441.jpg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p><strong>And every so often, we would even get a photo together:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598687472544-X504L88423CCHLXERB1L/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p><strong>No matter where we are or what we're doing, Amy is always down for a photo op. <em>She's my kind of girl.</em></strong></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
}